summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of One Thousand Dollars ($1,000.00), or so much thereof as may be necessary, to pay the necessary expense of the Corporation Counsel in the taking of testimony in Cause No. 1307 of the Circuit Court of the United States, for the Ninth Circuit, Western District of Washington, Northern Division, entitled William C. Osborne, et al, complainants, vs. The City of Seattle, A. C. Anderson, et al, Defendants.
